            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Choose a space within 4 spaces to place the rune of hope. Any friendly creature within 4 spaces of the rune is reduced to 0 hit points immediately gains 1d6 health and may take a major action. Each time a friendly creature uses the rune, you may choose to destroy the rune. All enemy creatures within 4 spaces of the rune must make an apposed willpower check against you. If they fail, they must make a major movement directly away from you (avoiding dangerous objects, cliffs, and such).",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Enhance: Increase the health regained by 1d6",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Enhance: Gain advantage on willpower checks associated to this spell",
